uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.reason

Class ORLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.reason.ORMonitor
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.reason.ORLogger
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ORClassifierLogger, ORMatcherLogger

    public abstract class ORLogger
extends ORMonitor
    Logger for ORClassifier and ORMatcher. Prints out information concerning OWL reasoning, including operation timings and, optionally, contents of requests and/or results.

    Timings printed out are:

    • Local time Time taken by last classification operation
    • Total time Time taken by all classification operations since monitor was last started
